name: The Secret Society of the Bad Monkey

metadata.name: Bad Monkey #1
metadata.description: The Secret Society of the Bad Monkey collection aren't just NFTs of cartoon monkeys, they are tickets to the Hustler Lifestyle. Owners are provided with prizes, perks and exclusive access to parties, conventions, giveaways and smoke sessions across the world allowing individuals to meet likeminded people & legends of the hustle. All of the Bad Monkeys begin their lives as hustlers but through our Racks upgrades they can be updated to Ballers or even Boss Monkeys. Each brand will be associated with a perk tied to the upgrade. All The Bad Monkey have access to The Bad Monkey Mansion in California. Free Access to token holders. Visit us at: www.badmonkeysociety.com for all the details!
